00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:42.170
of tens of millions of people around the world.

00:03:42.170 --> 00:03:46.130
They provide critical seafood for over a billion
people on the planet.

00:03:46.130 --> 00:03:51.240
Ninety percent of fishermen living on the
